OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy
OL,6,Facross southeast Scotland and
OL,7,Fnortheast England, especially near
OL,8,Fcoasts and this spreading inland
OL,9,Fovernight. Elsewhere, clear spells
OL,10,Fbring a chilly night with some mist
OL,11,Fand fog patches in prone spots,
OL,12,Fparticularly across parts of East
OL,13,FAnglia.
OL,14,
OL,15,CFriday:FEarly mist or fog clearing
OL,16,Finto a fine, warm day with light
OL,17,Fwinds. Sunny for most, though the far
OL,18,Fnorth and northwest turn cloudier and
OL,19,Fbreezier later with patchy rain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
